           <h4> Focused on Excellence and Learning </h4>
            <p>
           
Located in Aluva, Kochi amidst the backdrop of pristine surroundings and away from the bustling locales, Carmel School is one among the top cbse schools in Kochi today. The foundation of the school goes back to 1992 by ----- who wanted to create a learning environment that conveys academics beyond books. From academic foundation to development of your child’s intellectual and emotional personality, the school is all about an exceptional learning environ in true sense.

Carmel Schools expansive and modern campus includes some of the finest facility. These facilities are build to channelize your child’s holistic and social development to the fullest.
            </p>
            <h3>Our Core Values:</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"></i> Provide a safe, creative, and unique learning environment that consists of numerous curricular and extra-curricular opportunities</li>
              <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"></i> Promote a culture that fosters students to develop both intellectually and socially</li>
              <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"></i> Utilize latest teaching styles and facilities to let your child experience the fullest</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6 pt-4 pt-lg-0">
          <div class="icon-box">
              <center><h2><i class="ri-eye-fill" style="color: #e80368;"></i> 
              <strong>Vision</strong> </h2></center>
             
              <p> The vision of our school is to impart quality education to every student irrespective of their
          societal or pecuniary background. We believe that every student is unique and so are their
          learning needs. Therefore within the framework of these needs, teachers of Carmel
          School adapt to the learners educational practices and fosters enthusiasm and confidence in
          them. We are committed to the nurturing and development of each student of ours so that
          they achieve their full potential and become tomorrow’s resourceful citizens. </p>
            </div>
            <br>
            <div class="icon-box">
              <center><h2><i class="ri-rocket-fill" style="color: #e80368;"></i> 
              <strong>Mission</strong> </h2></center>
             
              <p> The purpose and mission of Cochin Public Schools educational program is to encourage, guide
          and empower elementary, middle and high school students to find their path through positive
          relationships. This way learners can achieve their highest aspirations and contribute to creating
          a better world. At the same time, the school also look forward to instill respect, love and
          compassion in children. We indeed adheres to provide a welcoming, safe and vibrant place
          students can trust second to their home. </p>
            </div>
            
